420
00:33:23,877 --> 00:33:25,879
<i>...outshined only by Sirius.</i>

421
00:33:26,046 --> 00:33:29,095
<i>And it's been ﬂipping out ever since.</i>

422
00:33:31,468 --> 00:33:36,599
<i>That dumbbell-shaped cloud
