423
00:33:41,102 --> 00:33:44,276
<i>At its center is one crazy star.</i>

424
00:33:44,439 --> 00:33:47,016
<i>Talk about unstable, Eta
Carinae is at least</i>

425
00:33:47,028 --> 00:33:49,616
<i>100 times more massive
